Package: NotSBS
Title: Narrowest-over-Threshold and Seeded Binary Segmentation for Change Point Detection in Factor Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yuqi", "Zhang", email = "yuqi.zhang@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the NotSBS procedure for detecting multiple change points in large approximate factor models. 
    The package provides simulation designs, model selection routines, plotting functions, and evaluation metrics inspired 
    by recent developments in high-dimensional structural change point analysis.
